//extra functions

int rec(int i1,int j1)
{
    if(i1+1<m&&!vis[i1+1][j1]&&c[i1+1][j1]=='f')
    {
        vis[i1+1][j1]=1;
        return 1;
    }
    if(i1+1<m&&!vis[i1+1][j1]&&c[i1+1][j1]=='b')
    {
        vis[i1+1][j1]=1;
        if(rec(i1+1,j1))
            return 1;
        vis[i1+1][j1]=0;
    }
    if(i1-1>=0&&!vis[i1-1][j1]&&c[i1-1][j1]=='f')
    {
        vis[i1-1][j1]=1;
        return 1;
    }
    if(i1-1>=0&&!vis[i1-1][j1]&&c[i1-1][j1]=='b')
    {
        vis[i1-1][j1]=1;
        if(rec(i1-1,j1))
            return 1;
        vis[i1-1][j1]=0;
    }
    if(j1+1<n&&!vis[i1][j1+1]&&c[i1][j1+1]=='f')
    {
        vis[i1][j1+1]=1;
        return 1;
    }
    if(j1+1<n&&!vis[i1][j1+1]&&c[i1][j1+1]=='b')
    {
        vis[i1][j1+1]=1;
        if(rec(i1,j1+1))
            return 1;
        vis[i1][j1+1]=0;
    }
    if(j1-1>=0&&!vis[i1][j1-1]&&c[i1][j1-1]=='f')
    {
        vis[i1][j1-1]=1;
        return 1;
    }
    if(j1-1>=0&&!vis[i1][j1-1]&&c[i1][j1-1]=='b')
    {
        vis[i1][j1-1]=1;
        if(rec(i1,j1-1))
            return 1;
        vis[i1][j1-1]=0;
    }
    return 0;    
}

//end of extra fnctions
